		expertise_en = '"The maiden from a land with history", used to be a model,Currently working as a costume designer, she has the illusion that she wants to become an Pokémon, and the butterfly-like clothes she wears are also worn to feel the mood of becoming Pokémon. P.S.: Cloth weigh 15 kilograms and worth s much as 200 huge gold beads',
